Name: schwannoma of ureter
Definition: An ureteral benign neoplasm that derives_from smooth muscle cells.

Name: mediastinal neurilemmoma
Definition: A uterine body mixed cancer that has_material_basis_in both endometrial carcinoma and sarcoma.

Name: obsolete metastatic ovarian small cell carcinoma with hypercalcemia
Definition: A uterine body mixed cancer that has_material_basis_in both endometrial carcinoma and sarcoma.

Name: neurilemmoma of the pleura
Definition: An endocrine organ benign neoplasm that is a benign tumor of the glandular type (adenoma) in the adrenal gland.

Name: schwannoma of jugular foramen
Definition: An astrocytoma that is characterized as a low grade astrocytoma and has_material_basis_in neoplastic astrocytes.
